                        <div class="Page-tile__hero-content-title">
        <h1 class="Page-tile__hero-content-title--medium">Climate Change</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="Page-tile__hero-content-description">
        <p><strong>Find out more about climate change, its effects and how World Vision is working to solve climate change through reforestation projects and other environmentally driven campaigns</strong></p>
    </div>

